BlueAlgae Distribution  is aimed to develop a simple Linux distro
building for embedded systems on x86, ARM, mips controllers with
latest features like
1. Embedded UI framework based on python
2. Framebuffer based backend
3. X11 based embedded framework
4. wayland based embedded framework
5. HTML5 support.
6. kiosk mode applications
7. Device Settings Framework
8. Remote upgradation Framework
9. Remote Control framework
10.Video and Audio conferencing capabilities. 

many more ......

BlueAlgae also  Release 4 versions of Linux live CD/DVD/USB stick 
distributions called
1. friction - distribution for mechanical/civil students
2. shock    - distribution for electrical and electronics engineers
3. strings  - music lovers linux distribution
4. vibes    - Digital signage linux platform.




